snippet.title: Men of War: Vietnam - Summer Trailer
snippet.description: Men of War: Vietnam is a new game for the critically acclaimed series. The new, story-driven campaign lets you taste the explosive mix of the jungle, Hueys and rock-n-roll in 1968.
